        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p>Last updated: March 2024</p>

        <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>Welcome to Word Alchemist. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our game.</p>

        <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We collect the following types of information:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Game scores and usernames for the leaderboard</li>
            <li>Analytics data about how you use the game</li>
            <li>Cookie preferences</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. How We Use Cookies</h2>
        <p>We use cookies to:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Remember your game preferences</li>
            <li>Store your high scores locally</li>
            <li>Analyze game usage through Google Analytics</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>4. Analytics</h2>
        <p>We use Google Analytics to understand how players interact with our game. This helps us improve the gaming experience. The analytics data is anonymized and does not personally identify you.</p>

        <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>Under GDPR, you have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Access your personal data</li>
            <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
            <li>Object to data processing</li>
            <li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>6. Contact</h2>
        <p>For any privacy-related questions, please contact us at privacy@wordalchemist.com</p>

        <h2>7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new policy on this page.</p>
